    <string name="settings_heartbeat_default_prompt">[HEARTBEAT] Lokhu ukuhlolwa kwezenzakalelayo. Buyekeza izinkumbulo zakho nemisebenzi esalindile. Uma konke kukuhle futhi akukho okudinga ukunakwa, phendula ngokuthe ngqo: HEARTBEAT_OK\nUma kukhona okudinga ukunakwa (izinkumbulo ezindala, imisebenzi esifikile, ukulandela komsebenzisi), kubhekane nakho.</string>
